open? Yeah, like he can't use Wikipedia because

00:06:23.143 --> 00:06:25.900
it's paralyzing. His, his weekend will be gone.

00:06:25.900 --> 00:06:29.640
&gt;&gt; What do you think about the portrayal of

00:06:29.640 --> 00:06:33.010
mental health in general, both in the media, and

00:06:33.010 --> 00:06:36.020
in society at large? How we deal with it as a

00:06:36.020 --> 00:06:40.060
population? Do you think we take mental health seriously? Do you think

00:06:40.060 --> 00:06:43.600
it's portrayed in a meaningful way that gets the right kind of

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:46.410
attention, or do you think we still have some work to do?

00:06:47.460 --> 00:06:52.840
&gt;&gt; I definitely believe that in the area of portrayal of mental health well,

00:06:52.840 --> 00:06:58.130
in the area of how the average person thinks of mental health, we have

00:06:58.130 --> 00:07:03.120
some work to do. Because it's one, it's, it's easy to look at someone and

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:08.330
say, you have a broken leg. You have a scratch. You've been burned. But when it

00:07:08.330 --> 00:07:12.200
permeates the mind. When it permeates the thing

00:07:12.200 --> 00:07:14.510
that's sitting behind the eyes, and looking back

00:07:14.510 --> 00:07:23.760
at you. It's hard to say, well you're an asshole versus you have an issue. And,

00:07:23.760 --> 00:07:26.080
because it's so difficult to recognize in the first

00:07:26.080 --> 00:07:32.600
place, we tend to overlook it, minimize it, and,

00:07:34.890 --> 00:07:38.200
and not give it the type of treatment that we should. If I had to have

00:07:38.200 --> 00:07:42.840
a message for somebody who's Bipolar II I

00:07:42.840 --> 00:07:47.020
would definitely say, seek medical assistance. this is

00:07:47.020 --> 00:07:51.310
something that responds very well to treatment. And

00:07:51.310 --> 00:07:53.560
once you've gotten that proper treatment, once you've

00:07:53.560 --> 00:07:56.040
been able to help yourself out, then you

00:07:56.040 --> 00:07:59.480
can live a very, very satisfying and happy life.

